OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1776503137
OL,3,CKittens rescued from crusher seconds
OL,4,Cbefore it was switched on
OL,6,FWatch: The kittens get used to their
OL,7,Ftemporary new home.
OL,9,FA litter of five abandoned kittens
OL,10,Fhave been rescued from a crusher on a
OL,11,Flandfill site in Wiltshire just
OL,12,Fmoments before it was switched on.
OL,14,FStaff at Crapper and Sons in Royal
OL,15,FWootton Bassett were checking the
OL,16,Fmachinery first thing in the morning
OL,17,Fwhen they noticed the kittens nestling
OL,18,Finside.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
