FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1776503137
OL,3,CKittens rescued from crusher seconds
OL,4,Cbefore it was switched on
OL,6,FThey called in a local cat rescue
OL,7,Fcentre, who are now looking after the
OL,8,Fcats.
OL,10,FMark Lambourne, who runs Shelter Paws
OL,11,FCat Rescue in Royal Wootton Bassett,
OL,12,Fsaid the animals owed their lives to
OL,13,Fthe staff at the landfill site, who
OL,14,Fwere carrying out their daily checks
OL,15,Fbefore switching on the crusher.
OL,17,FHe said: "The machine had been off for
OL,18,Fa few days. Before turning it back on,
OL,19,Fthey gave the machine a quick check
OL,20,Fover and saw the kittens and put them
OL,21,Fin a cardboard box.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1776503137
OL,3,CKittens rescued from crusher seconds
OL,4,Cbefore it was switched on
OL,6,F"I think they were probably born about
OL,7,Fa week ago and were a couple of days
OL,8,Fold when they were found. Their eyes
OL,9,Fhave just started to open now."
OL,11,FMark thinks the kittens - three males
OL,12,Fand two females - were born to a feral
OL,13,Fcat who thought it would be a safe
OL,14,Fplace to give birth. She wasn't with
OL,15,Fthe kittens when they were found.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1776503137
OL,3,CKittens rescued from crusher seconds
OL,4,Cbefore it was switched on
OL,6,FHe added: "They are being fed every
OL,7,Fthree hours at the moment through a
OL,8,Fsyringe with tiny amounts of milk.
OL,9,FThey're putting on weight and moving
OL,10,Faround, and when they get hungry they
OL,11,Fare very vocal which is good."
OL,13,FMark, who has been running the cat
OL,14,Frescue centre for the last ten years,
OL,15,Fexpects to keep the kittens for the
OL,16,Fnext ten weeks. They will then be
OL,17,Foffered to homes on condition the
OL,18,Fanimals are chipped and neutered.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
